In [65]:
def highlight_column(x):
    bl ='background-color:blue'
    yl ='background-color:yellow'
    rd ='background-color:red'
    gn ='background-color:green'
    sb ='background-color:skyblue'
    color=pd.DataFrame('',index=x.index,columns=x.columns)
    color.iloc[:,0]=bl
    color.iloc[:,2]=yl
    color.iloc[:,5]=rd
    color.iloc[:,7]=gn
    color.iloc[:,10]=sb
    
    return color

Invest.style.apply(highlight_column,axis=None)
